data.description: *Motivated seller, offers welcome* Welcome to your dream home! This impeccably maintained 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom ranch-style residence is a true gem that offers comfort, style, and convenience. Located just ten minutes from the prestigious Ft. Eisenhower. The fenced backyard provides a private oasis for relaxation and entertaining, offering a secure space for your loved ones, including furry friends, to enjoy the outdoors. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home. Schedule a showing today and experience the comfort, convenience, and charm that this property has to offer.
